Source: libgtk2-ex-splash-perl
Section: perl
Priority: optional
Build-Depends: cdbs, debhelper (>= 5)
Maintainer: Kevin Ryde <user42@zip.com.au>
Standards-Version: 3.9.1
Homepage: http://user42.tuxfamily.org/gtk2-ex-splash/index.html
Bugs: mailto:user42@zip.com.au

Package: libgtk2-ex-splash-perl
Architecture: all
Depends: perl (>= 5.8), libglib-perl (>= 1:1.220), libgtk2-perl, perl (>= 5.8), ${perl:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Temporary splash widget for Gtk2-Perl
 Gtk2::Ex::Splash displays an image splash on the screen either for
 program startup or a general way to flash something.  A little script
 is included to splash from the command line.
